```

---

## The Critical Ones
```
.env                ← your secrets — never commit this
*.db / *.sqlite     ← local database
uploads/            ← user resume files
node_modules/       ← 200MB+ of packages
__pycache__/        ← Python bytecode
models/             ← sentence-transformers downloads here
                       at runtime, can be 100MB+

resume_analyzer.db